Class ConstraintConjunction<V>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:

    Constraint<V>, Validation<V>

    public final class ConstraintConjunction<V>
extends ConstraintAggregation<V>
    This class provides ConstraintAggregation implementation that is conjunction of the encapsulated constraints. In other words this class represents logical AND operator.
